earning. This differs fundamentally from prior work by treating knowledge not as a resource to be retrieved, but as a *dynamic outcome of reasoning practice*. It bridges neural generation with symbolic evolution, offering a more cognitively plausible and scalable path toward trustworthy AI argumentation.

